The teacher should guide the learner in explaining;
• The meaning of the term "Business plan"
A business plan is a formal statement of a set of
business goals, why they are believed attainable
and the plans for reaching those goals.
• The components of a Business plan which are: -
- Executive summary,

- Production plan.

A business opportunity is a chance or a gap that exists

goods and services at a profit. It only exists when
there is acceptance to invest. Emphasize that not all
